 	  Enables support for Motorcomm network PHYs.
-	  Currently supports the YT8511, YT8521, YT8531S Gigabit Ethernet PHYs.
+	  Currently supports the YT8511, YT8521, YT8531, YT8531S Gigabit Ethernet PHYs.
 
